      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">1. Definitions</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">"Customer" means an individual or organisation seeking event services. "Vendor" means a registered service provider on Party Wings who offers services such as catering, decoration, photography, makeup, DJ, venue, rentals and similar services. "Booking" means a confirmed service engagement between a Customer and a Vendor facilitated through Party Wings.</p>

