      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">4. Booking, Payments & Fees</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
        <li>Bookings are agreements directly between Customers and Vendors. Party Wings may facilitate payments via third-party payment gateways. All transactions are subject to the payment gateway terms and fees.</li>
        <li>Party Wings may charge service fees, listing fees or platform commissions; fees will be disclosed at checkout or in Vendor agreements.</li>
        <li>Customers are responsible for paying the Vendor as agreed. Vendors are responsible for invoicing and any applicable taxes (GST) as per Indian tax law.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">5. Cancellation & Refunds</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">Cancellation policies vary by Vendor and service. Customers and Vendors should review the cancellation and refund terms before confirming a Booking. Party Wings may assist in disputes but is not automatically liable for refunds unless we have expressly accepted financial responsibility.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">6. Vendor Obligations</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
        <li>Vendors must provide accurate service descriptions, pricing, availability and contact information.</li>
        <li>Vendors must comply with all applicable laws, permits, safety and hygiene standards for the services they provide in India.</li>
        <li>Vendors are responsible for their staff, subcontractors and the quality of services delivered to Customers.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">7. Customer Responsibilities</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">Customers must provide accurate event details, site access and any necessary permits. Customers should discuss scope, deliverables and timelines with Vendors and obtain written agreements where appropriate.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">8. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">All content on the Platform (text, images, logos) is owned by Party Wings or licensed to us. Vendors grant Party Wings a non-exclusive license to display portfolio images and service descriptions on the Platform and related marketing. Do not upload content that infringes others' intellectual property rights.</p>

