      <p class="text-gray-700">Party Wings may suspend or terminate accounts that breach these Terms or applicable laws. Users may close their accounts by contacting support, subject to any outstanding obligations (such as pending bookings or payments).</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">14. Modifications to Terms</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">We may modify these Terms from time to time. We will post updated Terms on the Platform with a new effective date. Continued use of the Platform after changes constitutes acceptance of the revised Terms.</p>

